  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CAT
    Sample device specific accessor class.
    CATFactory
    Factory class for CAT sample service implementation
    Device
    Base of a JposDevice based implementation of JavaPOS CAT and ElectronicJournal device service implementations for the sample device implemented in SampleCAT.tcl.
    Device.DisplayOutput
    Class for processing terminal display information.
    Device.TicketOutput
    Class to process ticket data provided by the terminal to be printed on an attached printer.
    ElectronicJournal
    Sample device specific accessor class, bound to the credit authorization terminal service.
    ElectronicJournalFactory
    Factory class for ElectronicJournal sample service implementation
